

checking function(row)
  for loop to iterate through columns of each row
    check for base case: row number = n
      return board;

    place piece here
    check for conflicts
      if no conflicts,
        recursively call checking function(row+1) check if it === true
          if so, return true

    if we reached here, piece position is invalid
    unset piece

  if we get to this point, return false


